<p><FONT CLASS=Title3><b>2. <a name="Q2">Using the Mobhunter Site</a></b></font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>Besides providing news stories and links to other sites of interest, Mobhunter allows you to create multiple character profiles, manage a guild roster (currently in beta testing), and enter into discussion threads with other players. To use these aspects of our site, you should become a registered user.</font>
<p><FONT CLASS=Title4><a href="#top">Back to top</a></font>
