<p><FONT CLASS=Title3><b>3. <a name="Q3">Registering with Mobhunter</a></b></font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>Don't worry; this is quick and easy. Click the "Register" link and you will be taken to a screen that asks for a username, password, e-mail address, and name. We won't spam you or give out your information to anyone, ever--so don't be paranoid. We only ask for your e-mail address so that we can send you your password if you forget it and need it later.</font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>Note: Do not use your EverQuest Station ID and password when you register for Mobhunter! Make up something else-it's easy.</font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>Once you have registered, you should be logged in to Mobhunter. If not, you can do so manually. If your browser accepts cookies, our site will log you in automatically each time you visit.</font>
