<p><FONT CLASS=Title3><b>4. <a name="Q4">Logging in</a></b></font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>Pretty self-explanatory. Click the "Login" link and you will be asked for your username and password. Enter them correctly and you will be logged in.</font>
