<p><FONT CLASS=Title3><b>5. <a name="Q5">Menu Options</a></b></font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>When logged in, you have the following menu options on the left side of your screen:</font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4><b>Home</b> - Takes you to the Mobhunter Home page, no matter where you are on the site.</font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4><b>Help</b> - Takes you to this page (pretty neat, eh?).</font>
<br><FONT CLASS=Title4><b>Edit User Info</b> - Allows you to change your name (but not username), password, and e-mail address.</font>
<br><FONT CLASS=Title4><b>Log Out</b> - Logs you out of Mobhunter. Useful if you share a computer with someone else.</font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4><b>Contact Mobhunter</b> - Tells you how to get in touch with us.</font>
<br><FONT CLASS=Title4><b>Submit an Article</b> - Lets you submit news or an editorial for our consideration.</font>
<br><FONT CLASS=Title4><b>Submit a Link</b> - Allows you to submit a link to another site, which we may add to our list of links.</font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4><b>Add New Character</b> - Opens the Character Creation Wizard and allows you to enter character data. See below.</font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>When not logged in, you have less menu options, but may still read articles.</font>
