<p><FONT CLASS=Title3><b>6. <a name="Q6">Adding a Character Profile</a></b></font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>Mobhunter lets you manage multiple character profiles and allows you to interact with other users through any of your character names.</font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>Clicking the "Add New Character" link opens the Character Creation Wizard, which will guide you through the character creation process. When you're done, click "Finish" and your character data will be saved.</font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>You can add multiple characters on multiple servers. Go ahead and add characters to your heart's content. When you submit an article or reply to a news story, you can choose which character name you would like to use.</font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>Note: Mobhunter's character profiles are still in development. More functionality will be added soon.</font>
