<p><FONT CLASS=Title3><b>7. <a name="Q7">Replying to a News Story</a></b></font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>Mobhunter encourages community interaction through the use of discussion threads on the stories we publish. Every story has a "Reply to this Article" link at the bottom. If there is already discussion on a story, the threaded posts will appear below it. Click on a message title to read the post. Navigate through the discussion thread by clicking on the message titles.</font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>To add your response, click either "Reply to this Article" below the text of the story (which creates a new thread) or "Reply to this Message" if you want to keep your response in a thread that has already been created.</font>

<p><FONT CLASS=Title4>The Mobhunter staff does not want to play babysitter, so please use common courtesy-and common sense-when posting messages.</font>
